 drivers/net/phy/phylink.c | 68 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 include/linux/phylink.h   | 18 +++++++++++
 2 files changed, 77 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/net/phy/phylink.c
